1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-1068x710.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1592px) 100vw, 1592px" /></p><p>由比尔·斯卡斯加德和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fka-twigs">FKA Twigs</a>主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/music/the-crow-remake-starring-fka-twigs-has-reportedly-finished-filming-3322680">重启版<em>《乌鸦》</em></a>公布了一系列先睹为快的图片。</p><p>在这些照片中，斯卡斯加德扮演了哥特摇滚歌手埃里克·德拉文（Eric Draven），他对这个标志性角色的诠释是大量的黑色妆容、独特的纹身以及比原版电影已故明星布兰登·李（Brandon Lee）短得多的发型。在拍摄过程中因一场悲惨的现场事故而丧生。</p><p>即将上映的翻拍片由鲁珀特·桑德斯（ <em>《白雪公主与猎人</em>》、 <em>《攻壳机动队》）执导，</em>他告诉<a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/first-look-the-crow-flies-again-with-bill-skarsgard-and-fka-twigs" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《名利场》杂志</em></a>，他认为这部电影是对李的纪念的致敬，尽管它是对 1994 年恐怖复仇爱情片的全新演绎。故事。原版电影改编自詹姆斯·奥巴尔 1989 年的同名漫画系列。 </p><figure id="attachment_3594880" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594880" style="width: 1144px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594880" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bill-Skarsgard-in-The-Crow.jpg" alt="" width="1144" height="1390" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bill-Skarsgard-in-The-Crow.jpg 1144w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bill-Skarsgard-in-The-Crow-400x486.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bill-Skarsgard-in-The-Crow-800x972.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bill-Skarsgard-in-The-Crow-696x846.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Bill-Skarsgard-in-The-Crow-1068x1298.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1144px) 100vw, 1144px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594880" class="wp-caption-text">比尔·斯卡斯加德 (Bill Skarsgård) 在《乌鸦》重启版中饰演埃里克·德拉文 (Eric Draven)。图片来源：狮门影业</figcaption></figure><p>“布兰登是一个原创声音，我认为他将永远是<em>乌鸦</em>的代名词，我希望他为我们所做的事情以及我们如何再次带回这个故事感到自豪。他的灵魂在这部电影中非常活跃，”桑德斯说，并补充说斯卡斯加德给这个角色带来了一种“令人不安的美感”。</p><p> “他笔下的乌鸦有一种真正的脆弱和美丽，我认为比尔觉得他是这一点的继承者。”</p><p>即将重启的另外两张图片挑逗了埃里克和雪莉（FKA Twigs）的黑暗浪漫。第一张照片显示这对情侣在篝火旁亲密无间，而第二张照片则显示这对情侣隔着一层薄薄的白色面纱接吻。 </p><figure id="attachment_3594882" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594882" style="width: 2152px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594882" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2.jpg" alt="" width="2152" height="1418" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2.jpg 2152w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2-400x264.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2-800x527.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2-696x459.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2-1392x917.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-2-1068x704.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2152px) 100vw, 2152px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594882" class="wp-caption-text"> 《乌鸦》中的比尔·斯卡斯加德和 FKA Twigs。图片来源：狮门影业</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3594883" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594883" style="width: 2156px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594883" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3.jpg" alt="" width="2156" height="1420" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3.jpg 2156w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3-400x263.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3-800x527.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3-696x458.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3-1392x917.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/The-Crow-reboot-3-1068x703.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2156px) 100vw, 2156px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594883" class="wp-caption-text"> 《乌鸦》中的比尔·斯卡斯加德和 FKA Twigs。图片来