24/02/Justin-Timberlake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Justin-Timberlake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Justin-Timberlake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a>在其 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演日期中增加了一场额外的伦敦演出。请在下面查找门票详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/justin-timerlake-man-woods-review-2230941"><b>贾斯汀·汀布莱克——《林中人》评论</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手、词曲作者和前 *NSYNC 明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-announces-summer-2024-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3591839">上周（2 月 23 日）宣布了巡演的详细信息</a>，以庆祝他即将发行的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-announces-new-album-and-shares-romantic-comeback-single-selfish-3576962">《Everything I Thought It Was》</a> 。</p><p>这张 LP 将于 3 月 15 日通过 RCA 发行，并可在<a href="https://justintimberlake.lnk.to/EITIW-UK" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>预订，标志着他五年来的首张新专辑，其中将包含最近分享的单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-announces-new-album-and-shares-romantic-comeback-single-selfish-3576962">Selfish</a> ”、“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-debuts-new-song-sanctified-on-snl-3578292">Sanctified</a> ”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-announces-summer-2024-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3591839">“Drown”</a> 。</p><p>现在，由于门票需求旺盛，汀布莱克宣布为他即将在伦敦 O2 举行的英国和欧洲演出增加一场演出。</p><p>新的日期是 8 月 12 日，这也是这位歌手继前一天晚上在该场馆的第二次亮相。</p><p>此前宣布的其他英国演出包括 8 月 7 日在伯明翰 Utilita Arena 的演出和 8 月 8 日在曼彻斯特 Co-op Live 的演出。欧洲演出将于 7 月 26 日在克拉科夫开始，并于 9 月 6 日在里昂结束。</p><p>所有门票将于当地时间明天（3 月 1 日）上午 10 点开始发售，并可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fjustin-timberlake-tickets%2Fartist%2F847841" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。在下面的海报中找到英国演出的列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3594871" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594871" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594871" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600.jpg" alt="贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake) 更新了 2024 年英国巡演海报" width="2000" height="2602" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600-400x520.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600-800x1041.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600-696x905.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600-1392x1811.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Timberlake-tour-poster@2000x2600-1068x1389.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594871" class="wp-caption-text">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake) 更新了 2024 年英国巡演海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>最初的巡演日期清单是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-announces-free-one-off-london-show-buy-tickets-3588619">这位歌手上周（2 月 23 日）在伦敦 Roundhouse 举行的一次性演出</a>之前分享的，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlakes-one-off-london-show-tonight-cancelled-due-to-illness-3591859">后来因生病而取消</a>。</p><p>汀布莱克最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-announces-first-tour-in-five-years-forget-the-world-3577735">透露了他五年来首次巡演北美站的细节</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-extends-north-american-dates-for-2024-world-tour-3584293">由于需求旺盛，巡演很快就延长了</a>。目前该赛事定于 4 月 29 日在温哥华开幕，并持续到 7 月 9 日在列克星敦，并在 10 月和 11 月增加了一组额外的日期。北美演出的所有剩余门票都可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fjustin-timberlake-tickets%2Fartist%2F847841" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>找到。</p><p> 《Everything I Thought It Was》将是这位歌手自 2018 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/justin-timerlake-man-woods-review-2230941">《Man Of The Woods》以来的第一张专辑，</a> NME 称其为“王牌”：“老汀布莱克在各个方面都闪闪发光 - 你知道吗？我们仍然认为他是王牌。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，这位歌手最近与 *NSYNC 重聚，推出了他们的复出单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-new-nsync-song-better-place-3506369">“Better Place”</a> ，这是他们 20 多年来的第一首歌曲。歌手将这首歌描述<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-says-new-nsync-track-is-a-love-letter-to-fans-3498956">为“写给我们歌迷的情书”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-adds-extra-london-show-to-2024-uk-and-european-tour-3594869">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake) 为 2024 年英国和欧洲巡演增加了额外的伦敦演出，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《最后生还者》导演不确定他还能制作多少游戏https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-director-is-unsure-how-many-more-games-he-can-make-3594847?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=我们最后一位导演不确定他还能制作多少游戏Ryan EasbyThu, 29 Feb 2024 12:31:37 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3594847 <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p>开发商还谈到了《神秘海域2》的开发给顽皮狗带来了很大的压力</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-director-is-unsure-how-many-more-games-he-can-make-3594847">《最后生还者》的导演不确定他还能制作多少款</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发的游戏。</p> ; <p><img width="1252" height="795" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/the-last-of-us-new-project-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /></p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-last-of-us">《最后生还者》</a></em>导演尼尔·德鲁克曼谈到了他还能制作多少部大片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/final-fantasy-7-rebirth-review-3590691">《最终幻想 7 重生》评论：这部一流的重制版将带你进入云九</a></strong></li></ul><p>德鲁克曼在接受说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/logic">Logic</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jBesgXilHbk&amp;ab_channel=LogicallySpeaking" target="_blank" rel="noopener">采访</a>时谈到了他的不确定性，并解释了他如何发现导演大型比赛很累。</p><p> “我想我不会永远以这种规模做这件事。这只是很多，而且需要你付出很多。管理全球这么多人和多个工作室的压力非常大，”德鲁克曼在采访中说道。</p><p> “我知道时间有限，所以对我来说非常宝贵，当他们确实想和我在一起时，我不想浪费时间，这是第一位的。” </p><figure id="attachment_3571695" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3571695" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3571695" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review.jpg" alt="《最后生还者 第二部分 重制版》评论" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/The-Last-Of-Us-Part-2-Remastered-Review-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3571695" class="wp-caption-text"> 《最后生还者2》重制版。信用：顽皮狗。</figcaption></figure><p>在随后的采访中，德鲁克曼谈到了他开发<em>《神秘海域 2》的</em>经历，以及该游戏的成功如何给他和顽皮狗工作室带来了更大的压力。</p><p> “《<em>神秘海域 2》</em>是我制作过的所有游戏中最有趣的，因为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/uncharted">《神秘海域</a>1</em> 》有很多人喜欢它，但它并没有取得如此巨大的成功。它再次取得了足够的成功，我们让索尼高兴了，我们赚了足够的钱。”</p><p> “我记得我们也会在深夜玩多人游戏，只有这种友情，压力就不存在了，在<em>《神秘海域 2》</em>之后，一切都变得令人难以置信的压力，因为现在你不再飞行了在雷达之下，现在每个人都期待着一些伟大的事情。”</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/naughty-dog-teases-one-more-chapter-with-the-last-of-us-part-3-3582616">德鲁克曼还透露了该系列中的另一款游戏</a>，他在一部记录<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-last-of-us-part-ii">《最后生还者第二部》</a></em>开发过程的纪录片中表示，他觉得“这个故事可能还会有新的一章”。</p><p> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/god-of-war-ragnarok">《战神诸神黄昏》</a></em>的创意总监兼<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/god-of-war">《战神</a></em>2018》的游戏总监科里·巴尔罗格 (Cory Balrog) 引用了<a href="https://twitter.com/corybarlog/status/1762886077210374365" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a> （前 Twitter）上一篇报道采访的文章，写道“大同小异，兄弟”。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，有消息称一款<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/a-paranormal-activity-horror-game-is-in-the-works-3594802"><em>超自然活动</em>恐怖游戏</a>正在开发中。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-last-of-us-director-is-unsure-how-many-more-games-he-can-make-3594847">《最后生还者》的导演不确定他还能制作多少款</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发的游戏。</p> ;
